{"tid":837669,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【粵劇界白牡丹】粵劇名伶吳君麗離世，享年84歲。","createTime":"2018-09-26T14:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T09:01:23.000Z","uid":35221,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d93c43c6e20c98ba3eb84a044108b208ea699065","tid":837669,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180926/photo/bkn-20180926203625804-0926_00862_001_01b.jpg?20180926215449\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180926%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180926203625804-0926_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20180926215449&h=c01b5cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180926/photo/bkn-20180926203625804-0926_00862_001_02b.jpg?20180926215449\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180926%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180926203625804-0926_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20180926215449&h=9805f5d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳君麗（右）去年亦有露面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180926/photo/bkn-20180926203625804-0926_00862_001_03b.jpg?20180926215449\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180926%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180926203625804-0926_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20180926215449&h=192090f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳君麗與胡楓結伴出席薛家燕兒子的婚宴。<br />\n<br />\n粵劇名伶吳君麗突然傳出離世，享年84歲。粵劇已經瘋傳消息，譚炳文女兒譚淑瑩收到契媽呂林志嫦通知，而資深藝人丁羽亦指收到大律師朋友李偉民通知。而與吳君麗合作多年的拍檔胡楓接受東網訪問，他親證消息：「早兩日係探過佢，佢當期時喺瑪麗醫院，佢係病重，但咩病就唔知，我喺迎月嗰日去探佢嘅，佢當時瞓緊覺，到第二日中秋嗰日再去探佢，我見佢仲擘大眼，我有問佢認唔得認得我，佢只係眨咗一下眼，我見佢個樣好精神，唔係暴瘦，佢家人都同我講：『喺呢幾日㗎啦。』所以佢過身，我唔係好愕然。」<br />\n<br />\n粵劇名伶吳君麗離逝，享年84歲。吳君麗原名為吳燕雲，為「八牡丹」之一，她為「白牡丹」。薛家燕娶新抱時，吳君麗都有出席婚宴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180926/bkn-20180926203625804-0926_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180926%2Fbkn-20180926203625804-0926_00862_001.html&d=6AyKI7P%2BGQ6coZ8Cu2pPOeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=179d9671\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180926/bkn-20180926203625804-0926_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n安息 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0aedcc95cc028199b7b25e768cfb3c451a5d243","tid":837669,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:15:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dFiRGHJrBAY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdFiRGHJrBAY&d=6AyKI7P%2BGQ6coZ8Cu2pPOeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=caaf842b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dFiRGHJrBAY</a><br />\n<br />\n《青青河邊草》1966<br />\n胡楓、吳君麗、林鳳、林蛟、李香琴主演"},{"pid":"bf7acca0da7e72049ad955071ac91eb0d8ec01d7","tid":837669,"uid":116530,"like":10,"dislike":32,"score":-22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/221620_d98f932681775f22d969a8642a0d93ab.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F221620_d98f932681775f22d969a8642a0d93ab.gif&h=8b20f8a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dfc638e19589470cc68d923fa6ac340a71cd80c","tid":837669,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:18:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lk47AT2Tx9I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dlk47AT2Tx9I&d=6AyKI7P%2BGQ6coZ8Cu2pPOeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=2360942b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lk47AT2Tx9I</a><br />\n<br />\n《龍鳳爭掛帥》 1967<br />\n林家聲、吳君麗、關海山、李香琴 主演"},{"pid":"b02323bd495ee0b77fae3246af0b3abd8396e80c","tid":837669,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:20:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tUekl6ikRUo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtUekl6ikRUo&d=6AyKI7P%2BGQ6coZ8Cu2pPOeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=2b9117f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tUekl6ikRUo</a><br />\n<br />\n《遙遠的路》1967<br />\n吳君麗、李香琴、張英才、林蛟、杜平、鄧碧雲主演"},{"pid":"9396dd119a7ed412a5dc8c61ef9ae284aa8d8afe","tid":837669,"uid":32722,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bf7acca0da7e72049ad955071ac91eb0d8ec01d7","tid":837669,"uid":116530,"like":10,"dislike":32,"score":-22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/221620_d98f932681775f22d969a8642a0d93ab.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F221620_d98f932681775f22d969a8642a0d93ab.gif&h=8b20f8a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"唔好公開自己既無知"},{"pid":"bdabf7de8f14e2ddb7503d879042acaa2fc3abcc","tid":837669,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180926/large/1537970999_40c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180926%2Flarge%2F1537970999_40c1.jpg&h=b76a2186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【粵劇巨星殞落】吳君麗驚傳離世 享年84歲<br />\n<br />\n粵劇名伶吳君麗今晚突然傳出離世消息，享年84歲。原名吳燕雲的吳君麗，是影壇「八牡丹」之一，她獲封「白牡丹」。<br />\n<br />\n吳君麗早年居於上海，在抗日戰爭後隨母來港定居，曾跟廣東音樂「四大天王」之一尹自重學習粵曲，後來吳君麗加入陳非儂所辦的香江粵劇學院，成為陳非儂的「入室弟子」，有「玉喉艷旦」之譽。擅演青衣及刀馬旦，曾參與120部電影，包括粵劇電影及時裝電影。<br />\n<br />\n吳君麗於1962年成立「新麗聲影業公司」，直接參與電影拍攝工作。 1970年代至1980年代，參與林家聲的「頌新聲劇團」。1987年至1993年間，與陳劍聲、新海泉組織「新麗聲粵劇團」，並參與粵劇演出，1991年於新加坡舉辦個人演唱會。到2004年吳君麗將3000項服飾、戲箱、道具，以及劇本、宣傳刊物、照片等捐贈予香港文化博物館。<br />\n<br />\n已經甚少在幕前演出的吳君麗，於2008年，簽約無綫電視拍攝處境劇《畢打自己人》，2009年因滿約離開。而吳君麗對上一次出席公開場合，是出席薛家燕娶新抱的飲宴上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180926/58727434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F58727434&d=6AyKI7P%2BGQ6coZ8Cu2pPOeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=32ab315e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F58727434&h=8355bbd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180926/58727434</a>"},{"pid":"2d4fc1573d1f4fd3d880a5601faad8a0ba66bdd1","tid":837669,"uid":44454,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bf7acca0da7e72049ad955071ac91eb0d8ec01d7","tid":837669,"uid":116530,"like":10,"dislike":32,"score":-22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/221620_d98f932681775f22d969a8642a0d93ab.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F221620_d98f932681775f22d969a8642a0d93ab.gif&h=8b20f8a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"話明係粵劇名伶，你唔識唔好沖出嚟柒啦"},{"pid":"24fa5f633c8d1027185201d499dec42cf849bc34","tid":837669,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5052b0c629cc11a6fd9ff2ae5d78845badf8521","tid":837669,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"9396dd119a7ed412a5dc8c61ef9ae284aa8d8afe","tid":837669,"uid":32722,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bf7acca0da7e72049ad955071ac91eb0d8ec01d7","tid":837669,"uid":116530,"like":10,"dislike":32,"score":-22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/221620_d98f932681775f22d969a8642a0d93ab.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F2